{"type": "article", "id": 24241, "title": "青铜框架的精品酒店家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161156C8p7M2Hagt1GqZsy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这一套家具是洛杉矶的女设计师 Jenifer Janniere 为精品酒店设计的，一共五件，包括床、边桌、落地柜、壁挂式烛台和架子。她使用了一种旧的青铜，除了做结构外还充当了图案本身，它们斜向相交组成具有几何感的线条图案，是左右对称的，体现了一种传统与现代的结合，很有个性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161153rMZ1blLIgtRuqpih.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611534J9r0HTMjCbVzcN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161154jOiXH68Ikcpv7R3F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161154m3v0R8GESeIAfndP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061611560nZXoMdpy3LDwtVI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}